OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK virus research site left
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto deteriorate - MPs       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's main facility for dealing with
OL,6, viruses that jump from animals to      
OL,7, humans has been left to "deteriorate to
OL,8, an alarming extent," according to MPs. 
OL,10,FThe Public Affairs Committee report    
OL,11,Fcited "inadequate management and       
OL,12,Funder-investment" at the site in       
OL,13,FWeybridge.                             
OL,15,FIt said the Department for Environment,
OL,16,FFood & Rural Affairs (Defra) had       
OL,17,F"comprehensively failed in its         
OL,18,Fhistorical management" of the centre.  
OL,20,FDefra said work was already underway to
OL,21,Fupgrade the laboratories.              
